  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the cazuela over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the brown rice and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the green peas, lemon juice, feta cheese, salt, black pepper, and dried thyme, stirring to combine.",
    "Transfer the cazuela to the preheated oven and bake for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove the cazuela from the oven and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving."
